  <entry>
    <title>Video test</title>
    <url>/2021/09/15/Video-test/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<style>.bbplayer{width: 100%; max-width: 850px; margin: auto}</style><div class="bbplayer"><iframe class="bbplayer" id="mmedia-pGxRTOvFqZZyQvHr" src="https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV12K4y1W7vZ/&page=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=true" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="0" framespacing="0" sandbox="allow-top-navigation allow-same-origin allow-forms allow-scripts allow-popups"></iframe></div><script> document.getElementById("mmedia-pGxRTOvFqZZyQvHr").style.height=document.getElementById("mmedia-pGxRTOvFqZZyQvHr").scrollWidth*0.76+"px";
    window.onresize = function(){
      document.getElementById("mmedia-pGxRTOvFqZZyQvHr").style.height=document.getElementById("mmedia-pGxRTOvFqZZyQvHr").scrollWidth*0.76+"px";
    }; </script>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>配置项</th>
<th>默认</th>
<th>描述</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>bvid</td>
<td></td>
<td>视频 bv 号，bvid、aid 和 av 必填一项，推荐使用 bvid</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>aid</td>
<td></td>
<td>视频 av 号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>av</td>
<td></td>
<td>视频链接地址，不要带分 P 信息，与 aid 同时填写会被覆盖，不推荐使用</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>page</td>
<td>1</td>
<td>分 P，填写 av 时才会生效</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>quality</td>
<td>low</td>
<td>视频质量，可选 high low</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>danmaku</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>开启弹幕，带有此参数表示 true，不带表示 false</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>allowfullscreen</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>是否允许全屏</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>width</td>
<td>100%</td>
<td>宽度</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>height</td>
<td>500px</td>
<td>高度</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>margin</td>
<td>auto</td>
<td>位置，css 属性，例： “margin:auto” “margin:0 0 0 auto”</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>Reference&amp;Docuement: <a href="https://easyhexo.com/3-Plugins-use-and-config/3-5-hexo-tag-mmedia/#bilibili">https://easyhexo.com/3-Plugins-use-and-config/3-5-hexo-tag-mmedia/#bilibili</a></p>
]]></content>
